nodes.text: Greth Lan-Dwu Corporation was an energy company of Coruscant that owned a number of power-generating facilities across the entire planet. Anakin Skywalker and Obi-Wan Kenobi chased the Clawdite bounty hunter, Zam Wesell through one such facility after Wesell made an assassination attempt on Senator Padmé Amidala's life.
